Bukalapa encode username and password with Base64 (com->bukalapak->chatlib->util->Constant.class)
code : return Base64.encodeToString((paramString1 + ":" + paramString2).getBytes(),2);

Authenticate with Phone on this link (com->bukalapak->chatlib->service->AuthenticationService.class) :
"https://api.bukalapak.com/v2/users_simple.json"

Authentication for login in bukalapak on BASE_URL/authenticate.json with header (Authorization and "Using username&pass base64" with method POST)
request Token link : BASE_URL/users/tokens.json

Bukalapak's DB_NAME = BLCHATv3

SensorManager on android Application can drain the battery life for few hours. 
Sensors can't disable automatically when the screens turn off.
src:https://developer.android.com/reference/android/hardware/SensorManager.html

